<subSubSection pageId="50" pageNumber="51" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Inhabits the evergreen foothill forests and lower montane evergreen forests of the Amazon region from 1225-1720 m a.s.l. In the Andean region, it was registered in the montane cloud forests from 2000-2200 m a.s.l. Collected manually in horse feces and with canopy fogging methods.</paragraph>
